At my company we usually do a set of day 1 operations.
•	Configure persistent storage
•	Configure root certificate and wildcard certificate
•	Configure openshift API server certificate
•	Configure an IDP for authentication to the API
•	configure a way for user rbac (usually this is done via AD/LDAP and using ldapsyncconfig)
•	Label nodes
•	Install a set of operators, depending on needs
--	Cert manager
--	Sealed secrets
--	Elastic search operator
--	Redhat logging operator
•	Configure registry with persistent storage
•	Configure openshift monitoring
•	Configure openshift logging
•	Configure the ingress controller
•	Configure the web console
•	Configure project request template
•	Configure egress Network
